<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gamla taka awilo thim laka cheng te,
 Thagau simsen louh mang den thei ding haw;
 Kuoa chieh ding hukdamna thu gen dingin?
 Isu lam ena bang cheng thuok ngap di'n?

[V2]
 &quot;Thuneihna cheng cheng piek Ka hi!
 Thuneihna cheng cheng piek Ka hi!
 Gam tinah chieh unla Chanchin Pha thu gen un,
 Ngai un tel zel ingka&quot; A tii.

[V3]
 2. En un, khawvel kawt kihawng ah chiel na hiu,
 Krista sepaihte tho unla lut un;
 Kristiente halh un, theihtawp in pangkhawm un,
 Chanchin Pha'n gitloh hatkawl tan sak un!

[V4]
 3. &quot;Bang dinga halh lo?&quot; Pathien aw chun a tii,
 Bang dinga halh lo? tih thu gensawn un;
 Thil lauhum na'h hukdam di'n Isu a thii,
 Hinna, hukdamna thu chuh phuong zak un.

[V5]
 4. Namtin in, Pathien chuh lopi hen ti a,
 Guol zawhna la sak ding phat a nai tai;
 Tatsate hukdamna achun kipak un,
 Hallelujah, Lalpen ti'n kiko ding.</lyrics>
<title>&quot;GO YE INTO ALLTHE WORLD!&quot;</title>
<hymn_number>254</hymn_number>
</song>